<plot>Documentary about a famous Japanese rock musician, Cheep Hiroishi, takes a look back at his life over the last 20 years. Traveling back to the places he had been 2 decades before, he realizes how much time changes so many things. From Japan to New York, Cheep Hiroishi will share his history and his music.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?475472</url></doc>
